export default () => `

WHO WE ARE

Those of us in the gun and knife industry, whether consumer or vendor, know that it is getting pretty ridiculus to view product and sell/buy what we want. With all the red tape that the gun and knife industry has had to go through, there isn't a stress-free platform for products to be reviewed and purchased. This is where we come in....with a touch of all the social media platforms combined you can come in, take a look around, look a reviews and even purchase items you want. Just abide by the rules set and your transaction should be simple and stress-free.

`;
